Subject: AAD sync not updating group membership
Description:
Two users were added to their Azure AD group successfully (i.e. they automatically got added to the corresponding group in EPP) Feb 6 in the morning.  Another user was added in the afternoon, and EPP never added this third user to his group.

Also, the Last Synchronization field shows (blank) in the EPP console.
Solution_Comment__c: Sync errored out because a group was included that had been deleted.
